## Backup Recommendation
```bash
docker exec mysql sh -c 'mysqldump -uroot -p"$MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD" $MYSQL_DATABASE' > backup.sql
```

## Healthcheck
```bash
mysqladmin ping -uroot -p$MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD
```